---
title: Crispy Chicken Burger and Chorizo Chutney with homemade chips
description: Sometimes, opposites attract. In this recipe, for example, you'll find soft and warm brioche buns topping a crispy fried chicken burger, while sweet meets heat with a sweet chilli chorizo chutney in this adventurous and delicious dish.
